          sttl    Stand-alone System console Code - ACIA          pag     ** These are non-interrupt output routines for the system* console.*** systpc** Output the character in A.  X points to the port.  All* registers should be preserved.*systpc    pshs    a          save a reg2         lda     0,x        get acia status          bita    #ACTBSY    xmit busY?          beq     2b                  puls    a          get character          sta     1,x        output char          rts     return    ** sysrtt** Reset the console port.  X points to port.  Preserve all but A reg.*sysrtt    lda     #$03       reset code          sta     0,x                 lda     #$15       config byte          sta     0,x                 rts     return    